      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASSASSINO (3) goes very well here starting 10 times for four wins and two minors. Comes off a (28.94) win last time, scoring by one length in a Grade 5 over 498m at this track. Looks suited and should go close. EXOTIC RUBY (1) was out of the placings when seventh last time but prior to that produced a brilliant 21.74 win over 380m at this track. Expecting another bold showing. ASTON ELIJAH (2) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by a neck at this track in a handy 22.09 beating Mad Attitude. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Can measure up again. BULLEMOR BANNER (7) collected a minor prize last start over this track and distance - must be considered.",
